com.digev.mp.pipeline
Interface IWSInfo

Deprecated. Please see Message. 

public interface IWSInfo

The WSInfo interface defines the message context used to store all information related to processing a message in the Management Point. Instances of this interface are passed to all pipoeline (policy) components during both request and response processing.

disableAutoRespond

void disableAutoRespond(boolean disable)
Deprecated. 
Enable or disable the sending of a response by the Management Point.

Parameters:
disable - If true, no response to the incoming request will be sent by the Management Point. If false, the default, the Management Point will attempt to send the response message contained in this IWSInfo instance once processing has been completed.
